    <item>
      <title>Archive Utility not working on macOS</title>
      <link>https://kimpaper.github.io/en/posts/mac/2023-04-08-%EC%95%84%EC%B9%B4%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EC%9C%A0%ED%8B%B8%EB%A6%AC%ED%8B%B0-%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91-%EC%95%88%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-%ED%98%84%EC%83%81/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Apr 2023 01:05:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kimpaper.github.io/en/posts/mac/2023-04-08-%EC%95%84%EC%B9%B4%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EC%9C%A0%ED%8B%B8%EB%A6%AC%ED%8B%B0-%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91-%EC%95%88%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-%ED%98%84%EC%83%81/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Ran into this on a MacBook Air M2.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Archive Utility wouldn&amp;rsquo;t extract a zip on double-click. No idea why at first,
but the pattern was:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A leading digit in the filename.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;1_test.zip&lt;/code&gt; — would not extract
&lt;code&gt;test.zip&lt;/code&gt; — extracts fine&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Renaming the file made double-click extraction work again.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;1_test.zip&lt;/code&gt; also extracts if you use the &amp;ldquo;Extract&amp;rdquo; menu and pick a destination
folder manually.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maybe it was being detected as a multi-part archive?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Login with an ssh key</title>
      <link>https://kimpaper.github.io/en/posts/centos/2016-08-11-ssh-key-login/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Aug 2016 16:07:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kimpaper.github.io/en/posts/centos/2016-08-11-ssh-key-login/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Set up an ssh key on macOS so you can log into the server without typing a password&lt;br&gt;
&lt;del&gt;Normally I don&amp;rsquo;t do this, for security.&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;macos&#34;&gt;macOS&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;--generate-a-key&#34;&gt;- Generate a key&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;--view-the-public-key&#34;&gt;- View the public key&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;target-server-centos&#34;&gt;Target Server (CentOS)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;--add-the-public-key-to-the-sshauthorized_keys-file&#34;&gt;- Add the public key to the &lt;code&gt;~/.ssh/authorized_keys&lt;/code&gt; file&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;vi ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Installing homebrew on OSX 10.10.3</title>
      <link>https://kimpaper.github.io/en/posts/mac/2015-06-04-osx-10103-homebrew/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2015 01:05:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kimpaper.github.io/en/posts/mac/2015-06-04-osx-10103-homebrew/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Open a terminal and&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;ruby -e &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;gimjonghuiui-MacBook-Pro:bin paper$ brew -v
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Homebrew 0.9.5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;http://coolestguidesontheplanet.com/installing-homebrew-os-x-yosemite-10-10-package-manager-unix-apps/&#34;&gt;http://coolestguidesontheplanet.com/installing-homebrew-os-x-yosemite-10-10-package-manager-unix-apps/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
